                    <l n="b"> yasmin śāsati <lb n="B14" break="no"/> medinī-jaya-ramā-śrī-kīrttivāg-vallabhe</l>
                    <l n="c">taikṣṇya[ṃ/n] netra-yuge bhruvoś cala<lb n="B15" break="no"/>natā keśeṣu kārṣṇyan ta‡nau</l>
                    <l n="d">tanvīnān tanutābhavat· stana-yuge cānyonya<lb n="B16" break="no"/>-[saṃpī]ḍanam∙ ௳</l>
                </lg>
                
                <lg n="8" met="gīti">                    
                    <l n="ab">tasyābhūtān devyau kaṟṟaḷi-varaguṇa-samāhvaye satyau</l>
